reviewText: hello im 26 ive been boarding since I was 11 and I found this video very helpful and insightful it helped me on a lot of things deff recommend for beginner to advanced skater

My nephew said he liked it very much.  I bought it for him as a birthday present and he, and his friends watched it to help their skate boarding techniques improve.  He said he learned some new things.

This is a lot of fun to watch and informative. We purchased this and one other skateboarding dvd at the same time. As I parent I found the other video more informative but my children enjoy this one. It is faster paced and a bit more exciting than the one I like.
